@startuml archive-plan-architecture

title archive_plan — 模块架构 (4 子模块原子收口: precheck + ff-merge + archive-fs + cleanup)

' 节点名用日常术语优先,内部 module 名 / 函数名 / LOC / commit / REVIEW 引用见 INDEX

package "入口" as L1 {
  [MCP 入口 + 入口拦截\n(deny external)] as Entry
}

package "tool 实现" as L2 {
  [archive_plan facade\n(参数解析 + cwd 反查)] as Handler
  [收口业务层\n(4 子模块原子收口: precheck + ff-merge + archive-fs + cleanup\n+ post-ff-merge manual recovery)] as Impl
  [预检助手 + INDEX 同步助手] as Helpers
}

package "公共助手" as L3 {
  [fs/git 公共助手\n(4 个 tool 共享)] as SharedDeps
  [baton 收尾流程\n(关 teammate + 归档 caller)] as Baton
}

package "持久层" as L4 {
  [4 张数据表\n(会话 + 团队)] as Repos
  [会话管理器 + 事件总线] as SM
}

package "外部边界" as L5 {
  folder "主仓库 + worktree + ref/plans/\n+ ref/plans/<id>/spike-reports/" as Fs
  [git CLI 子进程] as Git
}

' ─── 调用链 ───

Entry --> Handler : 通过白名单后进 facade
Handler --> Repos : 反查 caller cwd + cwdReleaseMarker
Handler --> Impl : 进 4 子模块收口

Impl --> Helpers : runPrecheck 4 态笛卡尔 (plan/worktree/cwd/ff-merge)
Impl --> SharedDeps : 调 fs/git 公共助手

' 4 子模块原子收口 (facade 串联 runPrecheck → runFfMerge → runArchiveFs → runCleanup; 每阶段 error 短路)
' precheck Step 1-6.5 / ff-merge Step 7-8c / archive-fs Step 9-12.5 / cleanup Step 13-14
Impl --> Helpers : runPrecheck Step 1-6.5 (8 分支决策 + frontmatter parse + cross-check)
Impl --> Git : runFfMerge Step 7-8c (checkout base_branch + ff-merge worktree-<plan_id>)
Impl --> Fs : runArchiveFs Step 9-12.5 (改 plan frontmatter + mv plan + mv spike-reports/ + INDEX smart update + git add+commit)
Impl --> Repos : runCleanup Step 13 清 cwdReleaseMarker (commit 后提前清)
Impl --> Git : runCleanup Step 14 worktree remove + branch -D

Impl --> Handler : 返收口结果
Handler --> Baton : runBatonCleanup
Baton --> SM : phase 1 关 caller 同 team teammate
Baton --> Repos : phase 2 归档 caller session
Baton --> Handler : 返 cleanup 结果
Handler --> Entry : ok({archivedPath, plansIndexAction, archived, ...})

' ─── 关键不变量 ───

note bottom of Impl
  关键不变量:
  - 4 子模块原子收口: precheck → ff-merge → archive-fs → cleanup,每阶段 error 短路
  - 失败语义双段:
    · precheck / ff-merge 前失败 → 可 retry (4 entity 全停未变 + sessions 不动)
    · post-ff-merge 失败 (archive-fs / cleanup) → 进入 manual recovery,**无自动 rollback**
      (impl-archive-fs.ts:117-124 明文 "Cannot retry archive_plan as a whole",
       impl-ff-merge.ts:93-108 / impl-cleanup.ts:230-247 走 postFfMergeErr 给手工 cleanup hint)
  - cleanup Step 13 清 marker 提前到 commit 后 → Step 14 worktree remove/branch -D 失败时 marker 已清,
    caller 跑别 plan 不撞 stale marker reject
  失败兜底见 archive-plan-state-machine 图
end note

note bottom of SharedDeps
  fs/git 公共助手 (10 个)被 4 个 tool 共享
  (archive_plan / hand_off_session / enter_worktree / exit_worktree)
end note

@enduml
